<br>
I'll agree with the taunt and damage(somewhat). Too much taunt would make the game way to easy. Damage, I can accept that wars just arent meant to do damage, we're meant to tank.<br>
<br>
What I would really like to see is for the removal of the def disc and warriors placed on a seperate mitigation table based on AC. So if my ac was at 1410, I would get a 1% bonus, 1420, I would get a 2% bonus, etc... In effect making ac work again.<br>
<br>
Its hard to improve warriors tho, without trivializing the game. <p><p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12419" target="_BLANK">Arative</A><br> 
